  <h3>They Pick a Seed Company Based Only on Variety Count</h3>
  <p>
    More options do not help if timing information is weak.
  </p>

  <h3>They Do Not Match the Catalog to Their Planning Style</h3>
  <p>
    Some gardeners need stronger educational support. Others just need a better early-and-repeat crop selection.
  </p>
